### ============================================================
### Formula Service HTTP API 测试用例
### 服务地址: http://localhost:8081
### 基础路径: /api/v1/formula
### ============================================================

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 1. 验证接口 (POST /api/v1/formula/validate)
### ------------------------------------------------------------

### 1.1 验证合法公式 - 简单比较
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "ROE > 15"}

### 1.2 验证合法公式 - 复合条件
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "PE < 20 AND ROE > 15"}

### 1.3 验证合法公式 - 带函数调用
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "MA(CLOSE, 5) > MA(CLOSE, 20)"}

### 1.4 验证合法公式 - 复杂选股条件
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "CROSS(MA(CLOSE, 5), MA(CLOSE, 20)) AND VOL > REF(VOL, 1) * 1.5"}

### 1.5 验证非法公式 - 不存在的变量
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "UNKNOWN_VAR > 15"}

### 1.6 验证非法公式 - 不存在的函数
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "FAKE_FUNC(CLOSE, 5) > 10"}

### 1.7 验证非法公式 - 语法错误
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "ROE > "}

### 1.8 验证非法公式 - 参数数量错误
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "MA(CLOSE)"}

### 1.9 验证非法公式 - 类型不匹配
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "ABS(CLOSE)"}

### 1.10 请求体为空
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 1.11 请求体缺少 formula 字段
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"foo": "bar"}


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 2. 编译接口 (POST /api/v1/formula/compile)
### ------------------------------------------------------------

### 2.1 编译简单公式 - 返回 AST + 执行计划
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/compile
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "ROE > 15"}

### 2.2 编译带函数的公式
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/compile
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "MA(CLOSE, 5) > MA(CLOSE, 20)"}

### 2.3 编译交叉信号公式
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/compile
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "CROSS(MA(CLOSE, 5), MA(CLOSE, 20))"}

### 2.4 编译复杂选股公式
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/compile
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "CROSS(MA(CLOSE, 5), MA(CLOSE, 20)) AND VOL > REF(VOL, 1) * 1.5 AND PE < 30"}

### 2.5 编译布林带公式
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/compile
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "CLOSE > BOLL(CLOSE, 20, 2)"}

### 2.6 编译无效公式 - 未知变量
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/compile
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "UNKNOWN_VAR > 15"}

### 2.7 编译无效公式 - 语法错误
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/compile
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "ROE > "}


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 3. 获取 AST 接口 (POST /api/v1/formula/ast)
### ------------------------------------------------------------

### 3.1 获取简单公式的 AST
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/ast
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "ROE > 15"}

### 3.2 获取复合公式的 AST
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/ast
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "PE < 20 AND ROE > 15"}

### 3.3 获取带函数调用的 AST
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/ast
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "MA(CLOSE, 5) > MA(CLOSE, 20)"}

### 3.4 获取复杂公式的 AST
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/ast
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "CROSS(MA(CLOSE, 5), MA(CLOSE, 20)) AND VOL > REF(VOL, 1) * 1.5"}

### 3.5 获取无效公式的 AST（预期返回错误）
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/ast
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "UNKNOWN_VAR > 15"}


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 4. 列出所有函数 (GET /api/v1/formula/functions)
### ------------------------------------------------------------

### 4.1 获取所有可用函数列表
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/functions


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 5. 获取单个函数详情 (GET /api/v1/formula/functions/:name)
### ------------------------------------------------------------

### 5.1 获取 MA 函数详情
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/functions/MA

### 5.2 获取 EMA 函数详情
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/functions/EMA

### 5.3 获取 MACD 函数详情
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/functions/MACD

### 5.4 获取 RSI 函数详情
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/functions/RSI

### 5.5 获取 CROSS 函数详情
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/functions/CROSS

### 5.6 获取不存在的函数（预期 404）
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/functions/NONEXISTENT

### 5.7 函数名大小写不敏感测试
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/functions/ma


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 6. 综合场景 - 完整工作流
### ------------------------------------------------------------

### 6.1 场景：金叉选股 - 先验证再编译
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "CROSS(MA(CLOSE, 5), MA(CLOSE, 20)) AND VOL > REF(VOL, 1) * 2"}

### 6.2 场景：金叉选股 - 编译
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/compile
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "CROSS(MA(CLOSE, 5), MA(CLOSE, 20)) AND VOL > REF(VOL, 1) * 2"}

### 6.3 场景：超卖反弹 - RSI < 30 且放量
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "RSI(CLOSE, 14) < 30 AND VOL > AVG(VOL, 5) * 1.5"}

### 6.4 场景：超卖反弹 - 编译
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/compile
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "RSI(CLOSE, 14) < 30 AND VOL > AVG(VOL, 5) * 1.5"}

### 6.5 场景：均线多头排列
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "MA(CLOSE, 5) > MA(CLOSE, 10) AND MA(CLOSE, 10) > MA(CLOSE, 20) AND MA(CLOSE, 20) > MA(CLOSE, 60)"}

### 6.6 场景：均线多头排列 - 编译
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/compile
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "MA(CLOSE, 5) > MA(CLOSE, 10) AND MA(CLOSE, 10) > MA(CLOSE, 20) AND MA(CLOSE, 20) > MA(CLOSE, 60)"}

### 6.7 场景：基本面选股 - 低估值高增长
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "PE < 15 AND PB < 2 AND ROE > 15 AND RevenueGrowth > 20"}

### 6.8 场景：基本面选股 - 编译
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/compile
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "PE < 15 AND PB < 2 AND ROE > 15 AND RevenueGrowth > 20"}


### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 7. 赋值语法 & 多语句程序 (新增支持)
### ------------------------------------------------------------

### 7.1 简单赋值
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "Y1:=ROE>15; Y1"}

### 7.2 多语句赋值 - 编译
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/compile
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "Y1:=MA(C,5)>MA(C,20); Y2:=VOL>REF(VOL,1)*1.5; Y1 AND Y2"}

### 7.3 中文变量名 + 冒号命名结果
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "Y1:=MA(C,5)>MA(C,20); 结果: Y1"}

### 7.4 使用短变量别名 C/O/H/L/V
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "C>O AND H>REF(H,1) AND L<REF(L,1)"}

### 7.5 早晨之星 - 完整选股公式
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "Y1:=REF(C,2)<REF(O,2) AND (REF(O,2)-REF(C,2))/REF(C,2)*100>=2.5; Y2:=ABS(REF(C,1)-REF(O,1))/REF(O,1)*100<=1.5; Y3:=C>O AND (C-O)/O*100>=2.5 AND C>REF(C,2)+(REF(O,2)-REF(C,2))/2; 下跌趋势:=MA(C,5)<MA(C,10) AND MA(C,10)<MA(C,20); 早晨之星: Y1 AND Y2 AND Y3 AND 下跌趋势"}

### 7.6 早晨之星 - 编译
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/compile
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "Y1:=REF(C,2)<REF(O,2) AND (REF(O,2)-REF(C,2))/REF(C,2)*100>=2.5; Y2:=ABS(REF(C,1)-REF(O,1))/REF(O,1)*100<=1.5; Y3:=C>O AND (C-O)/O*100>=2.5 AND C>REF(C,2)+(REF(O,2)-REF(C,2))/2; 下跌趋势:=MA(C,5)<MA(C,10) AND MA(C,10)<MA(C,20); 早晨之星: Y1 AND Y2 AND Y3 AND 下跌趋势"}

### 7.7 获取早晨之星 AST
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/formula/ast
Content-Type: application/json

{"formula": "Y1:=REF(C,2)<REF(O,2) AND (REF(O,2)-REF(C,2))/REF(C,2)*100>=2.5; Y2:=ABS(REF(C,1)-REF(O,1))/REF(O,1)*100<=1.5; Y3:=C>O AND (C-O)/O*100>=2.5 AND C>REF(C,2)+(REF(O,2)-REF(C,2))/2; 下跌趋势:=MA(C,5)<MA(C,10) AND MA(C,10)<MA(C,20); 早晨之星: Y1 AND Y2 AND Y3 AND 下跌趋势"}
